data.meta_description:
171 likes, 4 comments - fanboy_expo on May 30, 2024: "We are thrilled to announce that Veronica Cartwright will be joining us in Orlando Sept 6-8 for Fanboy Expo Orlando. Veronica started as a child actor and can be seen in the original Twilight Zone and Alfred Hitchcock Presents as well as his classic The Birds. But most probably known her for her role as Lambert in The 1979 classic Alien. She can also be seen in Invasion of the Body Snatchers, The Right Stuff, The X-Files and more !
Get Tickets
www.fanboyexpo.com

#alien #alienmovie #thebirds #alfredhitchcock #twilightzone #invasionofthebodysnatchers #thexfiles #therightstuff #orlando #fanboy #fanboy2024 #fanboyexpo".
